TITLE: Basic Style Usage in Vanilla Extract CSS
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates basic usage of the style function to create a flex container class and its consumption in application code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract/blob/master/site/docs/api/style.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// styles.css.ts

import { style } from '@vanilla-extract/css';

export const flexContainer = style({
  display: 'flex'
});

// app.ts
import { flexContainer } from './styles.css.ts';

document.write(`
  <main class="${flexContainer}">
    ...
  </main>
`);
```

