TITLE: Applying Vanilla Extract CSS Styles to HTML Elements
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to import and apply Vanilla Extract CSS styles to HTML elements. This demonstrates the complete workflow from defining styles to using them in a component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract/blob/master/site/docs/overview/getting-started.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

