TITLE: Advanced Style Properties in Vanilla Extract CSS
DESCRIPTION: Shows advanced usage of the style function including CSS variables, pseudo-selectors, media queries, and feature queries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract/blob/master/site/docs/api/style.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// styles.css.ts

import { style, createVar } from '@vanilla-extract/css';

const scopedVar = createVar();

export const className = style({
  display: 'flex',
  vars: {
    [scopedVar]: 'green',
    '--global-variable': 'purple'
  },
  ':hover': {
    color: 'red'
  },
  selectors: {
    '&:nth-child(2n)': {
      background: '#fafafa'
    }
  },
  '@media': {
    'screen and (min-width: 768px)': {
      padding: 10
    }
  },
  '@supports': {
    '(display: grid)': {
      display: 'grid'
    }
  }
});
```

