TITLE: Adding support for calc nesting in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Version 0.1.1 introduced support for nested calc operations without requiring manual stringification, as shown in the diff example.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract/blob/master/packages/utils/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
-  calc('10px').add(calc('20px').subtract('4px').toString())
+  calc('10px').add(calc('20px').subtract('4px'))
```

