TITLE: TypeScript Module Import Example
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to import and use walkObject function from @vanilla-extract/private with module namespace objects, which previously caused runtime errors in vite-node.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract/blob/master/packages/private/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { walkObject } from '@vanilla-extract/private';
import * as ns from './foo';

// Runtime error in `vite-node`
walkObject(ns, myMappingFunction);
```

